{"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Rectangle\/fixedSize()"},"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"Fixes this view at its ideal size.","type":"text"}],"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Instance Method","modules":[{"name":"OpenSwiftUI","relatedModules":["OpenSwiftUICore"]}],"platforms":[{"name":"iOS","introducedAt":"13.0","beta":false,"deprecated":false,"unavailable":false},{"name":"macOS","introducedAt":"10.15","beta":false,"deprecated":false,"unavailable":false},{"name":"tvOS","introducedAt":"13.0","beta":false,"deprecated":false,"unavailable":false},{"name":"visionOS","introducedAt":"1.0","beta":false,"deprecated":false,"unavailable":false},{"name":"watchOS","introducedAt":"6.0","beta":false,"deprecated":false,"unavailable":false}],"title":"fixedSize()","role":"symbol","extendedModule":"OpenSwiftUICore","externalID":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore4ViewPAAE9fixedSizeQryF::SYNTHESIZED::s:15OpenSwiftUICore9RectangleV","remoteSource":{"fileName":"FixedSizeLayout.swift","url":"https:\/\/github.com\/OpenSwiftUIProject\/OpenSwiftUI\/blob\/main\/Sources\/OpenSwiftUICore\/Layout\/FixedSizeLayout.swift#L144"},"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"fixedSize"},{"kind":"text","text":"() -> "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"some"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"View","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore4ViewP"}],"symbolKind":"method"},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/openswiftui\/rectangle\/fixedsize()"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"nonisolated","kind":"attribute"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"fixedSize","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"() -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"some","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore4ViewP","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/View","text":"View","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":"\n","kind":"text"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"return-value","type":"heading","text":"Return Value","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A view that fixes this view at its ideal size."}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Discussion","level":2,"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"During the layout of the view hierarchy, each view proposes a size to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"each child view it contains. If the child view doesn’t need a fixed size"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"it can accept and conform to the size offered by the parent."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For example, a "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Text","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" view placed in an explicitly sized frame wraps"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and truncates its string to remain within its parent’s bounds:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["Text(\"A single line of text, too long to fit in a box.\")","    .frame(width: 200, height: 200)","    .border(Color.gray)"]},{"inlineContent":[],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"code":"fixedSize()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" modifier can be used to create a view that maintains"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"ideal size"}]},{"type":"text","text":" of its children both dimensions:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["Text(\"A single line of text, too long to fit in a box.\")","    .fixedSize()","    .frame(width: 200, height: 200)","    .border(Color.gray)"]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This can result in the view exceeding the parent’s bounds, which may or"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"may not be the effect you want."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You can think of "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"fixedSize()"},{"type":"text","text":" as the creation of a "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"counter proposal","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to the view size proposed to a view by its parent. The ideal size of a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"view, and the specific effects of "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"fixedSize()"},{"type":"text","text":" depends on the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"particular view and how you have configured it."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"To create a view that fixes the view’s size in either the horizontal or"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"vertical dimensions, see "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/View\/fixedSize(horizontal:vertical:)"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI","doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Rectangle"]]},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"references":{"doc://OpenSwiftUI/documentation/OpenSwiftUI/View":{"fragments":[{"text":"protocol","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"View","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"View","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"View","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A type that represents part of your app’s user interface and provides"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"modifiers that you use to configure views."}],"url":